00:19:24.040 --> 00:19:27.320
So, thinking about the RAM, I think it's important.

00:19:28.300 --> 00:19:31.920
So, I started working on this and said, well, what can I do?

00:19:32.000 --> 00:19:36.400
The starting point was 1,280 megabytes.

00:19:36.960 --> 00:19:43.000
And the little search daemon thing that I told you about, that once an hour, once every day, I can't remember the schedule.

00:19:43.140 --> 00:19:44.120
I think it's a few times a day.

00:19:44.500 --> 00:19:48.040
It'll pull all the content of Talk Python training and turn it into a search engine.

00:19:48.040 --> 00:19:53.720
So, like, you go over here and you're like, hey, I'm interested in, you know, taking some class.

